<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="17b" n="2">大田多稼ᅵ라</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="17b" n="2">大田에 稼ᅵ 한디라</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="17b" n="3">旣種旣戒야 旣備乃事니</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="17b" n="3">이믜 種며 이믜 戒야 이믜 備커 事니</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="17b" n="4">以我覃耜로 俶載南畝야</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="17b" n="4">내 覃 耜로  비로소 南畝애 載야</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="17b" n="5">播厥百穀니 旣庭且碩이라</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="17b" n="5">그 百穀 播니 이믜 庭고  碩디라</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="17b" n="6">曾孫是若이로다</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="17b" n="6">曾孫을 이 若놋다</sent>

<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="18a" n="1">旣方旣早며 旣堅旣孝ᅵ오</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="18a" n="1">이믜 方며 이믜 皁며 이믜 堅며 이믜 好고</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="18a" n="2">不稂不莠ᅵ어든</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="18a" n="2">稂티 아니며 莠티 아니커든</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="18a" n="3">去其螟螣과 及其蟊賊이라</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="18a" n="3">그 螟과 螣과 밋 그 蟊와 賊을 去야</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="18a" n="4">無害我田穉니</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="18a" n="4">우리 田엣 穉 害홈이 업리니</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="18a-18b" n="5">田祖有神은 秉畀炎火ᅵ어다</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="18a-18b" n="5">田祖의 神은 秉야 炎火에 畀홀디어다</sent><!--火^에-->

<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="18b" n="1">有渰萋萋야 興雨祁祁야</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="18b" n="1">渰히 萋萋야 雨 興홈을 祁祁히 야</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="18b" n="2">雨我公田이오 遂及我私야</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="18b" n="2">우리 公田에 雨고 드듸여 우리 私에 及야</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="18b" n="3">彼有不穫穉며 此有不歛穧며</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="18b" n="3">뎌의 擴디 아닌 穉 이시며 이예 斂티 아닌 穧 이시며</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="18b-19a" n="4">彼有遺秉며 此有滯穗니</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="18b-19a" n="4">뎌의 遺 秉이 이시며 이예 滯 穗ᅵ 이시니</sent><!--의 ^ 遺-->

<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="19a" n="1">伊寡婦之利로다</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="19a" n="1">寡婦의 利로다</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="19a" n="2">曾孫來止라 以其婦子로 饁彼南畝ᅵ어</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="19a" n="2">曾孫이 來디라 그 婦子로  뎌 南畝애 饁거</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="19a" n="3">田畯至喜로다</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="19a" n="3">田畯이 至야 喜놋다</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="19a-19b" n="4">來方禋祀야</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="19a-19b" n="4">來야 方에 禋祀야</sent><!--^야-->

<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="19b" n="1">以其騂黑과 與其黍稷으로 以享以祀니</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="19b" n="1">그 騂黑과 다믓 그 黍稷으로 以야  享며  祀니</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="19b" n="2">以介景福이로다</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="19b" n="2"> 큰 福을 介케 놋다</sent>
<sent type="title4" lang="chi" page="19b" n="3">大田 四章</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="19b" n="4">瞻彼洛矣혼 維水泱泱이로다</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="19b" n="4">뎌 洛을 瞻혼 水ᅵ 泱泱도다</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="19b-20a" n="5">君子至止시니 福祿如茨ᅵ로다</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="19b-20a" n="5">君子ᅵ 至시니 福祿이 茨 도다</sent><!--^도-->

<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="20a" n="1">韎韐有奭니 以作六師ᅵ로다</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="20a" n="1">韎 韐이 奭니  六師 作놋다</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="20a" n="2">瞻彼洛矣혼 維水泱泱이로다</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="20a" n="2">뎌 洛을 瞻혼 水ᅵ 泱泱도다</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="20a" n="3">君子至止시니 鞞琫有珌이로다</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="20a" n="3">君子ᅵ 至시니 鞞에 琫고 珌얏도다</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="20a" n="4">君子萬年애 保其家室이로다</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="20a" n="4">君子ᅵ 萬年애 그 家室을 保리로다</sent>

<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="20b" n="1">瞻彼洛矣혼 維水泱泱이로다</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="20b" n="1">뎌 洛을 瞻혼 水ᅵ 泱泱도다</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="20b" n="2">君子至止시니 福祿旣同이로다</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="20b" n="2">君子ᅵ 至시니 福福이 이믜 同도다</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="20b" n="3">君子萬年애 保其家邦이로다</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="20b" n="3">君子ᅵ 萬年애 그 家邦을 保리로다</sent>
<sent type="title4" lang="chi" page="20b" n="4">瞻彼洛矣 三章</sent>

<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="21a" n="1">裳裳者華여 其葉湑兮로다</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="21a" n="1">裳裳 華ᅵ여 그 葉이 湑도다</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="21a" n="2">我覯之子호니 我心寫兮로다</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="21a" n="2">내 之子 覯호니 내 이 寫도다</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="21a" n="3">我心寫兮호니 是以有譽處兮로다</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="21a" n="3">내 암이 寫호니 일로  譽ᅵ며 處ᅵ 잇도다</sent>

<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="21b" n="1">裳裳者華여 芸其黃矣로다</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="21b" n="1">裳裳 華ᅵ여 그 芸히 그 黃도다</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="21b" n="2">我覯之子호니 維其有章矣로다</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="21b" n="2">내 之子 覯호니 그 章이 잇도다</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="21b" n="3">維其有章矣니 是以有慶矣로다</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="21b" n="3">그 章이 이시니 일로  慶이 잇도다</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="21b" n="4">裳裳者華여 或黃或白이로다</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="21b" n="4">裳裳 華ᅵ여 或 黃며 或 白도다</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="21b-22a" n="5">我覯之子호니 乘其四駱이로다</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="21b-22a" n="5">내 之子 覯호니 그 四駱을 乘얏도다</sent><!--駱^을-->

<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="22a" n="1">乘其四駱니 六轡沃若이로다</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="22a" n="1">그 四駱을 乘니 六轡ᅵ 沃若도다</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="22a" n="2">左之左之예 君子宜之며</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="22a" n="2">左며 左홈애 君子ᅵ 宜며</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="22a" n="3">右之右之예 君子有之로다</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="22a" n="3">右며 右홈애 君子ᅵ 有도다</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="22a" n="4">維其有之라 是以似之로다</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="22a" n="4">그 有디라 이러모로  似도다</sent>
<sent type="title4" lang="chi" page="22a" n="5">裳裳者華 四章</sent>

